      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "As I watched my dog running toward me, I felt like I had seen this scene
    countless times before. Memories came flooding back like a rushing spring, and
    I remembered all the moments we had spent relying on each other. I\u2019m so
    happy to meet you again, and I know we will share many more joyful memories in
    the future.\r\n\r\nAnd finally, thank you to you\u2014the one who helped me find
    my dog.\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
